1 _DSCR A gathering at the Adams Place George W Adams is 4th from L his wife is the lady with the white head shawl Sarah Jane Johnson Adams. The lady squatted down in middle is their daughter Margaret Adams Tackett. The little girl peeping over her head i
2 CONC s Florence Adams Swindall (her father is John Wallace Adams..son of George and Sarah J. Johnson Adams) Two more children of John Wallace Adams are the little boy in the front with the suspenders and his name is John Wesley Adams. His sister is behi
2 CONC nd him and Sarah Jane Johnson Adams has her hand on her shoulder and her name is Sarah Jane Adams Mullins. Another sibling of these children is to the R of the little boy with suspenders and his name is William "Chub" Adams. The boy to the R of Wil
2 CONC liam "Chub" Adams is their cousin William Potter. Back row 4th person from the R is George and Sarah Jane Johnson's daughter, Clarissa "Rissie" Adams Little with her husband to "her" R (Lafe Little)
