1 _META <metadataxml><content><line>&lt;p align="left"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Richard Branham, Sr. of Yorkshire, England&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align="left"&gt;Richard Branham was born&amp;nbsp;1644 in West Riding, Yorkshire, England. Richard grew up in l
2 CONC uxury; as his father is reputed to have been a Knight of the Realm. Richard immigrated before 10/1665 to Virginia for profit, receiving land from the sovereign, Charles II&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align="left"&gt;In about 1688 in Rappahannock Co VA, Richar
2 CONC d married Deborah Haslock b. c. 1645 in England.&amp;nbsp;Richard and Deborah lived their lives in Rappahannock Co VA. But, Deborah died before 1691 in Rappahannock Co VA.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</line></content></metadataxml>
